px;\">\n      <li>Your project is now discoverable in the {{$json.data.category}} section</li>\n      <li>Community members can like, comment, and share your work</li>\n      <li>Track performance in your creator dashboard</li>\n      <li>Consider upgrading to Creator tier for advanced analytics</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div style=\"text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 30px;\">\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n      <a href=\"https://shonen-ark.com/account/creator\" style=\"color: #d4af37; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px;\">üìä Creator Dashboard</a>\n      <a href=\"https://shonen-ark.com/upload\" style=\"color: #d4af37; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px;\">‚¨ÜÔ∏è Upload More</a>\n      <a href=\"https://discord.gg/shonen-ark\" style=\"color: #d4af37; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px;\">üí¨ Join Community</a>\n    </div>\n    \n    <p style=\"color: #666666; font-size: 12px; margin: 20px 0 0 0;\">¬© 2025 Shonen Ark. Keep creating amazing content! üå∏</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
